Oluwatosin "Tosin" Otubajo (amụrụ na 16 Julaị 1984) bụ onye Naijirịa bụbu onye na-agba bọọlụ nke gbara dịka onye na-echebe ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Naijiria.

Otubajo bụ nwa afọ Ajegunle, Lagos, ma na-egwuri egwu dị ka onye na-agbachitere Flying Angel, Vero Bims Queens Lagos, Confluence Queens na Bayelsa Queens. Ọ bụ onye otu mba Naijirịa, a gụnyekwara ya na ogige ọzụzụ Naijirịa maka 2000 Summer Olympics na Sydney, Australia. Otú ọ dị, e mechara wepụ ya na ndị otu ahụ
Afọ asatọ ka e mesịrị, a gụnyere ya na ndị otu Naijirịa na 2008 Summer Olympics dị ka onye ọzọ na-egwu egwuregwu.
